Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.96,0:00:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要有点刺激才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.27,0:00:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算吃海苔时噎到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.21,0:00:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是盯著摄影机看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.17,0:00:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,摆出明星架式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.61,0:01:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题 V手势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.58,0:01:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使 Rock'n'Roll
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.38,0:01:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老套的乐园(啊摇摆摇摆)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.45,0:01:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旋转的宇宙也在跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.15,0:01:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火力全开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.06,0:01:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,摇摇摆摆跳一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.03,0:01:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(啊摇摆摇摆)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.13,0:01:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都会变成天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.30,0:01:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.58,0:01:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警报?出了什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.58,0:01:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，到底出了什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.92,0:01:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火灾，发生火灾了 天使室烧起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.26,0:01:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花?情况怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.33,0:01:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷的房间…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.40,0:01:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，薄荷，等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.00,0:01:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在回房间很危险喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.12,0:02:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#19燃烧系伤心油炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.00,0:02:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷的情况怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.30,0:02:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还在哭，这已经是第三天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.61,0:02:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直关在房里，好像也没吃什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.11,0:02:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么办?这样下去薄荷会病倒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.02,0:02:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仅次於香草，第二冷静沉著的薄荷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.98,0:02:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然会乱成这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.75,0:02:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是很重要的东西被烧掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.99,0:03:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说的也是，饭也不吃一直哭个不停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.33,0:03:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此事非比寻常啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.13,0:03:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁都会有比自己的生命更重要的东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.37,0:03:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.74,0:03:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事到如今更不能讲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，我们这几个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.01,0:03:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.54,0:03:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.75,0:03:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我炸天妇罗的油烧起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.15,0:03:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在清枪的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.72,0:03:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不小心走火引发爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.49,0:03:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,针灸的火居然烧到了沙发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.42,0:03:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果一发不可收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.73,0:03:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草的是，那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神的怒火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.44,0:03:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哭声停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.24,0:03:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.17,0:03:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她稍微冷静下来了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.74,0:03:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们还是等她自己出来看看她的样子再说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.15,0:03:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.78,0:03:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.99,0:04:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,丧失了比自己生命更重要的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.42,0:04:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有那么简单重新站起来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.26,0:04:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像也有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.49,0:04:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.43,0:04:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷，不要做傻事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.33,0:04:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请放开我!求求你们让我死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.03,0:04:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.50,0:04:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不知道什么东西烧了\N可是也不至於寻死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.94,0:04:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们是不会明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.01,0:04:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我来说那是无可取代的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.78,0:04:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我苟且偷生活在没有它的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.11,0:04:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我宁愿就这样死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.28,0:04:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请振作一点，薄荷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.35,0:04:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真糟糕，照这样下去薄荷真的会完蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.10,0:04:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她不是早就完蛋了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.36,0:04:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之，虽然不晓得她的什么宝贝烧掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.30,0:04:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，失去的东西不会再回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.40,0:04:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然这样，不如早点让她把那个东西忘了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.94,0:04:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞧你说得自信满满\N你有什么办法吗?兰花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.24,0:04:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然，请包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.08,0:05:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，你叫薄荷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.11,0:05:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你住在哪里呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.25,0:05:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次我要搭我父亲的船出海\N薄荷要不要去啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.39,0:05:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花，现在的我没心情参加这种聚会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.49,0:05:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要想那么多啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.45,0:05:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女生最重要的还是谈恋爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.46,0:05:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找个帅哥把过去的事通通忘掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.93,0:05:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我办不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.53,0:05:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让各位久等了，这是整条的红烧银河灯笼鱼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.64,0:05:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安．．．安迪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.33,0:05:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来你平安无事啊，我的安迪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.92,0:05:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷，你在干什么?还有，安迪是谁啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.39,0:05:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，像那天一样温柔的拥抱我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.06,0:05:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下来请包在我身土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.76,0:05:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，请吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.48,0:05:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多吃一点好吃的甜点，把难过的事都忘掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.30,0:05:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷，你看这是我的自信杰作喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.77,0:06:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，怪兽的中间还有一只熊猫喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.11,0:06:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么看都像是被怪兽吃掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.78,0:06:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之，吃吃看吧，薄荷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.45,0:06:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可洛太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.76,0:06:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，这个蛮好吃的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.04,0:06:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷，你怎么了?我做的饼乾不好吃吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.62,0:06:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，轮到你出场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.19,0:06:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么都不要想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.52,0:06:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把过去的一切全部抛弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.09,0:06:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将你的心交给神吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.96,0:06:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求神问佛啊，没办法\N因为她的情况相当严重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.63,0:07:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，你在看什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.64,0:07:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷已经升天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.57,0:07:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要死啊，薄荷回来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.71,0:07:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醒醒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.94,0:07:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.28,0:07:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，真是不可思议的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.64,0:07:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死掉的大家在向我招手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.35,0:07:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下喔，我马上就来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.25,0:07:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然无法让她那么简单就忘记啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.96,0:07:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对薄荷来说那场火灾不是过去的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.16,0:07:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以烧掉的东西没有回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.39,0:07:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯人没有找到的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.96,0:07:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能一辈子都会这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.06,0:07:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，大家出来自首好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.07,0:07:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说我们是那场火灾的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.90,0:07:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要\N不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.34,0:07:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.01,0:07:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不能让她这样下去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.48,0:07:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那还是自首吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.91,0:07:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯…啊，对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.71,0:07:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想到什么了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.78,0:07:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊，确实是个好办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.32,0:07:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷，不得了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.26,0:07:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你听我们说，不要吓到喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.76,0:08:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关於上次的火灾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.09,0:08:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本说原因是配电器短路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.80,0:08:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事实上不是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.76,0:08:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是有人故意纵火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.97,0:08:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,纵火?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.30,0:08:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，那天在你的房间旁边看到一个可疑的人影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.04,0:08:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个人应该就是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.61,0:08:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说给我听，详细一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.63,0:08:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特征呢?长相呢?什么都好，请告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快说快说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.45,0:08:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我记得头上有长角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.69,0:08:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有长角是吗，其它呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.42,0:08:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其它啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.96,0:08:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在想起来了背上有长翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.33,0:08:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.36,0:08:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊对啊，我也想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.17,0:08:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脸颊还有个十字刀伤还有尾巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耳朵是猫耳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.44,0:08:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有，右手是一只穿孔机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.71,0:08:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且是可以自由拆下替换的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.64,0:08:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，你也讲你知道的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.64,0:08:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?我想想看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.35,0:09:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他最喜欢吃的是布丁而且还叫自己”玛洛”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.19,0:09:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,头长得像西瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.66,0:09:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有裸著上身打领带，穿运动短裤跟木屐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.36,0:09:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走路还会走三步退两步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.06,0:09:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且眼睛还会发出雷射扫描光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.43,0:09:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有，还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.53,0:09:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用磁铁合体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.47,0:09:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之，不像是这世界会有的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.22,0:09:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊，对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.23,0:09:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了，画好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.18,0:09:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.35,0:09:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本不可能有这种人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.55,0:09:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是有啦！  就是有啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.95,0:09:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，好惊人喔 薄荷你画得好像喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.69,0:09:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.66,0:09:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的，真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为实在太像了我看了都冷汗直流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶的臭家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.26,0:09:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然把我宝贝的夥伴们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.47,0:09:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我立刻去分析这张画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.97,0:09:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙就是夺走我一切的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.08,0:09:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，他根本不是人\N这种滥家伙不配当人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.97,0:10:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等著吧！我一定会把你找出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.62,0:10:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把你打入十八层地狱永不超生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.99,0:10:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了，好像成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.08,0:10:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷变得那么有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.77,0:10:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样她应该不会想死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.47,0:10:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，这样不要紧吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.56,0:10:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,万一真的有人长得像那张画里的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.53,0:10:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情就严重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.55,0:10:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别傻了，不可能有这种怪胎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.94,0:10:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,娃拉娃拉星人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.98,0:10:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玛洛最喜欢吃布丁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.91,0:10:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玛洛最喜欢吃布丁  各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.32,0:10:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里禁止外人进入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.95,0:10:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请赶快回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.59,0:10:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的有耶，而且还很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.73,0:10:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这里见到我算你们倒霉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.30,0:10:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.33,0:10:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下，薄荷这些人不是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.74,0:10:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你们要妨碍我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.50,0:11:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是你们我也不会手软喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.91,0:11:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要把你们全都杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.58,0:11:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.64,0:11:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，原来你们都在这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.55,0:11:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关於前几天你们引起的火灾一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.42,0:11:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你们必须负责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.39,0:11:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以下个月的薪水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.59,0:11:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.47,0:11:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才的话，我全部都听到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.40,0:11:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这该怎么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.54,0:11:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总归一句话，你们就是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.91,0:11:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,时间差不多到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.94,0:11:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，请大家相信下次还能见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.05,0:11:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Adieu(法文”永别了”)Adios(西班牙文”永别了)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.25,0:11:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Amig。(西班牙文”我的朋友”)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.72,0:11:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我的双兔耳剪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.99,0:11:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猜拳十三奥义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.69,0:11:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始罗，剪刀石头布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.96,0:11:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.36,0:11:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要掌控敌人的电脑胜利就是必然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.49,0:11:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,命运是可以预测的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.33,0:12:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是榻榻米吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.68,0:12:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.11,0:12:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大小刚刚好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.48,0:12:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直少了一张榻榻米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.62,0:12:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶，怎么这么大?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.69,0:12:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种东西坠落地面的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.62,0:12:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，预测坠落地点算出来了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.36,0:12:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，大约在TB地区255区那一带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.76,0:12:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好避开了人口密集的区域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.13,0:12:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流了一身汗好舒服喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.14,0:12:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等，那是什么?怎么往这里飞过来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.34,0:12:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么会发光?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.12,0:12:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厉害我还是第一次看到陨石坠落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.62,0:12:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底是什么东西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.66,0:13:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#20搞笑灯芯草的红烧鲤鱼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.70,0:13:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,错不了的，这是遗失文明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.47,0:13:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?这张榻榻米吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.34,0:13:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,榻榻米形状的遗失文明还真的很少见啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.57,0:13:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎样，多亏有这家伙你才捡了一条命回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.08,0:13:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是捡到实了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.55,0:13:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这张榻榻米有防御一切攻击的护身能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.02,0:13:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以防止意外死亡和怪异猝死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.02,0:13:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以死的很安稳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.62,0:13:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为什么不早说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.44,0:13:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有，你为什么不会被弹出去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么好笑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.40,0:13:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我不太懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.53,0:13:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，你真的很厉害耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.94,0:13:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.31,0:13:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托，完全没有用耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.38,0:13:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开炮开炮!把它打烂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.58,0:13:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.06,0:14:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你蛮好用的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.26,0:14:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我暂时把你放在家里好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.34,0:14:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好暖和喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.58,0:14:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不能飞快一点吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.98,0:14:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌啦大家的纹章机都跟丢了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.65,0:14:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这下该怎么办?如果迷路的话都是你害的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.49,0:14:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.96,0:14:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，你不要紧吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.51,0:14:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，我迟到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.44,0:14:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花，你在干什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.14,0:14:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遗失文明已经回收完毕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.24,0:14:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会迟到又不是我造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.91,0:15:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，既然任务结束了我们早点回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.78,0:15:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家等等我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.02,0:15:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在这里等我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.12,0:15:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.66,0:15:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然想闯入女生厕所   你在想什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.47,0:15:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花，茶泡好了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.14,0:15:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，请?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.37,0:15:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.68,0:15:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，兰花你这张臭脸要摆到什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.22,0:15:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会变成这种脸都是这张榻榻米害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.22,0:15:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它帮了你很多忙是张很棒的榻榻米啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪里棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.76,0:15:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顽固，不懂得通融，又保守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.29,0:15:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本就是一张无聊透顶的榻榻米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.50,0:15:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌，为什么只因为可以不用撑伞这个理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就变成买东西部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.04,0:16:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些都是你害的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.26,0:16:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那张榻榻米到底要缠我到什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.75,0:16:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那位性感小猫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.99,0:16:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在躲雨吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.25,0:16:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要上车啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.18,0:16:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的高级跑车不用担心下雨喔，来吧来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.59,0:16:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用客气，没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.42,0:16:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，怎么办好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.43,0:16:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，不好意思你有伴是不是?性感小猫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.50,0:16:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有我根本不认识这张榻榻米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.57,0:16:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就恭敬不如从命罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.77,0:16:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，好耶，不用客气尽管跟我撒娇吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.45,0:16:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.15,0:16:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么去那么久啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为发生了很多事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.32,0:16:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,榻榻米先回来了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.59,0:16:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被雨淋得湿答答的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.39,0:16:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,淋得湿答答的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.29,0:16:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本是在装可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.56,0:16:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它明明可以防止被雨淋的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.30,0:17:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为人而做出来的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.93,0:17:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它的能力和存在价值只会为了那个人而存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.56,0:17:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以兰花不在的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.91,0:17:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它不会为了自己使用那些能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.14,0:17:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本就是想叫我欠它人情嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.66,0:17:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样?甜心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.33,0:17:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,划船约会也很可爱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.23,0:17:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的耶对健康好像也很有帮助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.30,0:17:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊，健康最重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.73,0:17:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.77,0:17:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天鹅不抽菸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.11,0:17:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甜心，你在看什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.71,0:17:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么来，我们继续划吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像这样骑著机车兜风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.09,0:17:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心情就会跟山谷一起跳起吉特巴舞的舞步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.49,0:17:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.43,0:18:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用担心，这条路就像放在我家院子里的盆栽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.70,0:18:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好帅喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.57,0:18:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.70,0:18:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是叫你不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.47,0:18:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Darling，快抓住我的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.94,0:18:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抓不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.01,0:18:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Darling
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.91,0:18:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作一点，Darling
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.62,0:18:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水鸟低下头去，沉入池底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.75,0:18:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Darling
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.56,0:18:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?为什么你不肯救我的Darling?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.69,0:18:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再也不想看到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.40,0:18:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我滚远一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.17,0:18:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恭喜你了，兰花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.31,0:18:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说对方是个家里有点小钱的小开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.41,0:18:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且也蠢得刚刚好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.65,0:18:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你终於找到理想对象了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.05,0:18:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.69,0:19:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在照顾他的伤势这段期间两人的感情越来越好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.01,0:19:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么嘛 它干嘛真的离开啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.68,0:19:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.78,0:19:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的好漂亮喔，兰花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.32,0:19:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你，梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.39,0:19:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了，重要的新郎官怎么还没来呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.16,0:19:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他突然有点急事现在应该已经搭飞机来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.06,0:19:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心爱的甜心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.63,0:19:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上就能得到你甜蜜的心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.67,0:19:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位旅客请注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.41,0:19:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在本机的引擎有一具故障
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.71,0:20:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是本机一共搭载了四具引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.91,0:20:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此对飞行没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.34,0:20:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若有熟悉机械的旅客请尽速与空服人员联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.06,0:20:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不得了了，兰花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.09,0:20:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你未婚夫搭乘的飞机好像就要坠机了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.43,0:20:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的运气一向很好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.07,0:20:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我这个号称学校史上最蠢的学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.54,0:20:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能像现在这样坐在机长的座位上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.25,0:20:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就表示我的运气真的很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.58,0:20:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那架，高度一直在下降畔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.25,0:20:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那已经没救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.72,0:20:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Darling，Darling不要死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.32,0:20:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，榻榻米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.10,0:20:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,榻榻米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.08,0:21:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你，榻榻米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.02,0:21:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直没有注意到你有多么体贴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.32,0:21:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不需要六张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.96,0:21:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不需要四张半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.13,0:21:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只要你这一张就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.13,0:21:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了?榻榻米?你哪里坏掉了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.13,0:21:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么开始消失了呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.54,0:21:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，我们好不容易才和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.54,0:21:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下来才要开始的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.34,0:21:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.43,0:21:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,榻榻米消失後已经过了一个礼拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.12,0:22:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它是为了什么而出现为了什么而消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.90,0:22:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.00,0:22:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有一件事能够确定那就是我开始在夜晚散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.79,0:22:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机长，你怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.49,0:22:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劫机．．．劫机不够啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.13,0:22:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得了劫机缺乏症
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.56,0:22:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机长!机长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.40,0:22:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有谁是吗?旅客当中有没有劫机客?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.70,0:22:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有没有谁是劫机客?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.17,0:22:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是劫机客，有什么事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.48,0:22:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逮捕起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.38,0:22:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来是陷阱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.38,0:22:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,启动认真模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.78,0:22:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.22,0:22:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超very紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.78,0:22:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心儿呯呯跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.32,0:22:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,私奔极限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.39,0:23:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秘密进入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.96,0:23:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宛如软绵绵的蛋白霜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.13,0:23:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心跳加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.53,0:23:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冰淇淋派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.04,0:23:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吻了你的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.21,0:23:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快要溢出来的Jelly Beans
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.24,0:23:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拥抱五彩缤纷的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.38,0:23:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将音调调至Pop
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.18,0:23:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚采收的新鲜鼓动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.52,0:23:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昧地空转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.76,0:23:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活力爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.13,0:23:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(下一回也有神明指示)

